Hi Andy,
That is the oversized hub for engine cases damaged where the pulley slides in 
and thusly the case is machined to a bigger diameter and then requires the 
oversized pulley hub to keep the engine oil from leaking out there due to 
internal air pressure inside the case.
Eric&Barb
